{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"025cde2b12","title":"右派言论——攻击、丑化党员","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"134b4f855b","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"025cde2b12"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"0ca27306bb","name":"贾佑庸"},{"id":"273c2ef95f","name":"阎林森"},{"id":"2f80c7277e","name":"冯国大"},{"id":"8a2ec21f47","name":"汤伯森"},{"id":"9bfff4ae55","name":"尹毅夫"},{"id":"d3ab465caa","name":"北京矿业学院"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"b0a7653ba3","type":"title","text":"右派言论——攻击、丑化党员","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"025cde2b12"},{"id":"05ba7e62bd","type":"authors","text":"北京矿业学院阎林森贾佑庸冯国大汤伯森尹毅夫","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"025cde2b12"},{"id":"ac0b9efdc3","type":"paragraph","text":"“党员执行党的方针政策，执行党的指示，党员是木头人，不会独立思考，党员和组织的关系好比狗和主人，主人给些吃的就跟着跑，而不管它主人是好是坏，都是忠诚的。”（北京矿业学院  阎林森）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"025cde2b12"},{"id":"cb76bfb0dd","type":"paragraph","text":"“党员使人望而生畏，党的门禁森严，难以靠近是党群关系恶化的原因。”（北京矿业学院  贾佑庸）","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"025cde2b12"},{"id":"4b5b96f6ed","type":"paragraph","text":"“党几年来培养了一批盲目的崇拜者，说着清一色的话，包庇党的错误，党员只听上级领导布置，而不开动脑筋，不追求真理。”（北京矿业学院　冯国大）","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"025cde2b12"},{"id":"8bc49044ca","type":"paragraph","text":"“党团员都是挂牌的，其目的是为了找爱人，向上爬。”（北京矿业学院  汤伯森）","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"025cde2b12"},{"id":"6fca266174","type":"paragraph","text":"“党员威风凛凛出现于群众面前，批评别人是能手，整别人思想是家常使饭。”（北京矿业学院  一枝梅）","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"025cde2b12"},{"id":"9f79bb6b9c","type":"paragraph","text":"“毛主席是土包子，党团员是混旦，王八旦，拍马溜须的人，是坐探，走狗，和特务。”（北京矿业学院　尹毅夫）","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"025cde2b12"},{"id":"33d430c022","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《高等学校右派言论选编》（中共中国人民大学委员会，1958年8月）。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"025cde2b12"}],"page":{"id":"db363299ea","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"025cde2b12","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}